SUMMARY:Sound Healing Meditation
DTSTAMP:20260620T130314Z
DTSTART:20260621T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Step into a deeper stillness inside the spacious and tranquil B
	uffalo Bayou Park Cistern. \nOffered in collaboration with UNIONisCREATION
	™\, this meditation and sound experience invites guests into a space of re
	sonance\, restoration\, and inner alignment. Through gentle vibrations of 
	singing bowls\, wind chimes\, and a gong\, along with guided awareness\, p
	articipants are supported in reconnecting body and mind. \nThis series is 
	more than meditation – it is a practice of listening\, feeling\, and retur
	ning to center within one of Houston’s most iconic\, immersive spaces. Eac
	h session unfolds as a shared moment of reflection\, connection\, and soun
	d-guided stillness. \nGuests should bring their own cushions or mats. No f
	ood or drinks are allowed inside the Cistern. \nCost: $20 \nPURCHASE TICKE
	TS\n\nhttps://buffalobayou.org/event/sound-healing-meditation-284/\n\nFrom
	 Buffalo Bayou Partnership
URL:https://buffalobayou.org/event/sound-healing-meditation-284/
LOCATION:BUFFALO BAYOU PARK CISTERN\, 105 Sabine Street\, Houston\, TX\, 77
	007\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:buffalo-bayou-partnership
CATEGORIES:Buffalo Bayou Partnership
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
