DESCRIPTION:As part of this summer’s Kicking It at Hermann Park offerings\,
	 enjoy “Moonlight Movie Nights\,” presented by Goya\, in the Commons! On F
	riday\, July 3\, join us for a showing of National Treasure (2004 | PG | 2
	h 10m runtime). \nThe movie will start at approximately 8:30 p.m.\, around
	 sunset. The movie showing is free and open to the public. \nBe sure to ge
	t to the Commons early to snag your spot on the lawn. Guests are welcome t
	o bring blankets or lawn chairs to settle in for the movie. \nFood and bev
	erage will be available for purchase at the cafe and with food vendors on-
	site. \nThank you to Goya for their generous support!\n\nhttps://hermannpa
	rk.org/event/moonlight-movie-nights-national-treasure/\n\nFrom Hermann Par
