UID:Yn8P5fWuYAFOr-ie5IFPT
SUMMARY:Second Saturday Bird Survey
DTSTAMP:20260620T130314Z
DTSTART:20260711T080000Z
DESCRIPTION:2nd Saturday of the month8:00 – 10:00 amFree\, but donations ap
	preciatedAll ages\, minors must be accompanied by an adult \n\n\n\nMeet in
	 front of the Nature Center building \n\n\n\nWork on your bird watching sk
	ills while helping the Arboretum monitor bird populations on a fun\, relax
	ed morning walk. Join us on the second Saturday of each month in the court
	yard behind the building for a two-hour bird survey led by Arboretum staff
	 members\, Kelsey Low and Theo Ostler. We welcome all levels of bird watch
	ing skill and all ages (as long as you’re quiet) – but no dogs\, please! I
	f you have binoculars of your own\, please bring them. We have a limited n
	umber of binoculars available to borrow. \n\n\n\nThe June 13\, 2026 Bird S
	urvey has been cancelled. Please join us in July!\n\nhttps://houstonarbore
	tum.org/event/second-saturday-bird-survey/2026-07-11/\n\nFrom Houston Arbo
	retum & Nature Center
URL:https://houstonarboretum.org/event/second-saturday-bird-survey/2026-07-
	11/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-arboretum
CATEGORIES:Houston Arboretum & Nature Center
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
