DESCRIPTION:Doors: 6pm Earlybirds Club is a dance party for women and gende
	r expansive folks that starts at 6pm and ends at 10pm ? because we have sh
	*t to do in the mornin DJ Caribbeats spins the songs that live in your bon
	es: 80s\, 90s\, and 2000s pop\, hip-hop\, new wave\, and R&B. But Earlybir
	ds Club is more than a night out. It?s a permission slip to take up space.
	 To be loud\, weird\, wild\, sweaty\, sparkly\, sentimental\, and complete
	ly yourself. It?s a judgment-free dance floor built on joy\, kindness\, co
	nnection\, and the shared understanding that sensible footwear is a love l
	anguage. And because joy is even better when it gives back\, 10% of ticket
	 proceeds go to the Susie Lee Legacy Fund\, supporting nonprofits that upl
	ift women\, gender-expansive people\, and communities who need it most. Th
	is show is 21+ All General Admission Tickets are Standing Room only IMPORT
	ANT: WHITE OAK MUSIC HALL IS A CASHLESS VENUE. Please be sure to bring a d
	ebit or credit card.\nDoors: 6pm Earlybirds Club is a dance party for wome
	n and gender expansive folks that starts at 6pm and ends at 10pm ? because
	 we have sh*t to do in the mornin DJ Caribbeats spins the songs that live 
	in your bones: 80s\, 90s\, and 2000s pop\, hip-hop\, new wave\, and R&B. B
	ut Earlybirds Club is more than a night out. It?s a permission slip to tak
	e up space. To be loud\, weird\, wild\, sweaty\, sparkly\, sentimental\, a
	nd completely yourself. It?s a judgment-free dance floor built on joy\, ki
	ndness\, connection\, and the shared understanding that sensible footwear 
	is a love language. And because joy is even better when it gives back\, 10
	% of ticket proceeds go to the Susie Lee Legacy Fund\, supporting nonprofi
	ts that uplift women\, gender-expansive people\, and communities who need 
